      "review_summary": "The PR adds a Mattermost client helper for `GET /posts/{postId}/thread`, seeds cold thread history before inbound context construction, and adds client unit coverage.\n\nPR surface: Source +61, Tests +59. Total +120 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level. Current main stores Mattermost thread history in a process-local map and builds context from that map, so after restart/session clear the cold-thread path has no server backfill before dispatch.",
